        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">[Mockup Generator Placeholder]</h2>
          <p style="max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <strong>TODO:</strong> Implement interactive WebGL or Canvas-based product visualizer here. 
            This will be an Astro Island using <code>client:visible</code> to ensure heavy assets only load when needed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>